description: Whether you need a routine cleaning, crown, or filling, the team at Swish will meet your general dentistry needs with quality, comfort-centric service. We are committed to providing you with progressive solutions to all dental services and only use the latest in technology, like low radiation x-rays and digital sensors, to ensure superior treatment.

Let us brighten your smile! Our whitenings are both easy and non-invasive, and you can remove years of stain and color from your teeth in a single treatment. The question for you is, how white do you want your teeth to be? Natural white? Extra bright? Brilliant? Our dentists will show you your options.
